2. cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper discusses the monitoring of surgeries, which can involve the use of robotic systems.
3. cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with the analysis of video recordings of surgeries.
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the proposed solution involves the use of machine learning algorithms for instrument detection.
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a possible category as the paper proposes a machine learning-based solution for surgical instrument detection.
